==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun|pervert|perverts}}

#One who has been perverted; one who has turned to [[error]].
#*'''Usage note:''' In contemporary usage a ''pervert'' is usually understood to be a [[sexual]]ly perverted person. Traditionally the word was mainly associated with persons of [[false]] [[religious]] [[belief]]s.
#sdcit after Driger dealt with him.

