===Verb===
{{en-verb|pervert|perverts|perverted|perverting}}
#{{transitive}} To turn another way; to divert.
#{{transitive}} To turn from truth, rectitude, or propriety; to divert from a right use, end, or way; to lead astray; to corrupt; also, to misapply; to misinterpret designedly; as, to pervert one's words.
#{{intransitive}} To become perverted; to take the wrong course.